            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <h2>Spector's patient monitoring system is not your ordinary GPS system.</h2>
                    <p class="lead">Are you serving patients or taking care of a loved one at home who tends to wander?  Various GPS products on the market claim to be the perfect solution to the problem, but with the expensive initial cost of the equipment in addition to the mandatory monthly fees, these products are not economically appropriate for most households, let alone hospitals or long-term care facilities with dozens of patients.  Spector Inc. presents a low cost alternative where the only equipment needed are any devices with bluetooth function and a beacon sticker.  As tablets and iPads are readily available to most families and healthcare organizations, the cost of the monitoring a patient is reduced to only $10 per year.</p>
                </div>
